---
title: Spiced Chicken & Garlicky Asparagus Salad with Roasted Potatoes & Creamy Pesto Dressing
description: Tonight’s tender chicken is calling our name - lightly spiced, juicy and steaming hot, we can’t resist! Simple sides are the best accompaniments, like golden, roasted chunks of potato and some garlicky greens. Alright, we’re done explaining, you can dive in now!

